                            <textFieldCell key="cell" id="Ghb-Lr-PMV">
                                <font key="font" metaFont="system" size="15"/>
                                <string key="title">When using ^⌘C (collecting) and ^⌘V (replaying) the clipboard is in Batch Clipboard's special _batch mode_ where items you copy get stored, then when you paste them one-at-a-time they replay the same order.</string>
