                                <font key="font" metaFont="system" size="15"/>
                                <string key="title">Collecting into the batch with ^⌘C increases the count in the menu bar, replaying them by pasting with ^⌘V decreses the count. When the last item is pasted the icon returns to an outline and the clipboard returns to normal.</string>
